Roman fold shades, also known as gravity fed shades, are used in manyÂ Solar Innovations<sup>Â®</sup>' conservatories and sunrooms. Gravity fed shades are typically used on sloped roofs but can also be utilized in vertical wall applications. These shades are individually sized to fit between the rafters of an interior glass roof and are operated with a motor or manual pull cord in a Roman fold style. Numerous materials and colors are available.

